  "text": "In order to facilitate estimation of the impact of the educational policy reform in question on the observed scholastic achievements attained by the students in the G12 and G13 groups, some additional specification is required. In addition to the pooled data, the grades were also sorted by gender, g = {pooled, female, male}. [CITATION_1] matrix D consists of eleven columns of dummy variables that identify the school in which the grades were earned (there are twelve schools in the sample and school number eleven is taken as the reference), and, finally, the matrix P contains certain relevant personal characteristics describing the students involved.",
